## Principles

- Lead with education and trust
- Keep audience problems specific
- Use AI to support structure, speed and clarity
- Review AI outputs before using them
- Avoid exaggerated or unsafe health claims
- Use affiliate links only when relevant to the audience need
- Treat digital products as structured support, not quick promotion
- Improve workflows based on feedback and performance

